# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:23
msgid "Learn More"
msgstr "詳しくはこちら"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:24
msgid ""
"We are working hard to expand this user guide and to improve OpenShot Video "
"Editor, but if you are stuck and don't know where to turn, OpenShot has "
"several sources for additional information."
msgstr ""
"私たちはこのユーザーガイドの拡充とOpenShot Video "
"Editorの改善に努めていますが、行き詰まってしまった場合は、OpenShotには追加情報を得られるいくつかの情報源があります。"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:27
msgid ""
"OpenShot has several `YouTube Tutorials "
"<https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_"
" available to help you learn more."
msgstr ""
"OpenShotには、より詳しく学べる`YouTubeチュートリアル "
"<https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_"
" がいくつか用意されています。 `YouTube Tutorials "
"<https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:28
msgid ""
"OpenShot has a `Reddit User Community <https://openshot.org/forum>`_ "
"dedicated to users helping users, answering questions, and discussing video "
"editing and OpenShot topics."
msgstr ""
"OpenShotには、ユーザー同士が助け合い、質問に答え、ビデオ編集やOpenShotに関する話題を議論するための`Redditユーザーコミュニティ "
"<https://openshot.org/forum>`_ があります。 `Reddit User Community "
"<https://openshot.org/forum>`_"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:29
msgid ""
"If you would like to help improve this User Guide, `view source on GitHub "
"<https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tree/develop/doc>`_."
msgstr ""
"このユーザーガイドの改善に協力したい場合は、`GitHubでソースを見る <https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-"
"qt/tree/develop/doc>`_ ことができます。 `view source on GitHub "
"<https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tree/develop/doc>`_"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:30
msgid ""
"If you have discovered a new bug, please `Report a Bug "
"<https://www.openshot.org/issues/new/>`_."
msgstr ""
"新しいバグを発見した場合は、`バグを報告する <https://www.openshot.org/issues/new/>`_ ようお願いします。 "
"`Report a Bug <https://www.openshot.org/issues/new/>`_"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:31
msgid ""
"If you need professional support, you can open a ticket by sending an "
"message to support@openshot.org or `Schedule a call "
"<https://calendly.com/openshot-support/desktop>`_."
msgstr ""
"プロフェッショナルなサポートが必要な場合は、support@openshot.org にメッセージを送るか、`通話を予約する "
"<https://calendly.com/openshot-support/desktop>`_ ことでチケットを開くことができます。 "
"`Schedule a call <https://calendly.com/openshot-support/desktop>`_"
